{% call components.section("Accessibility") -%}

  <h4 style="margin-top: -4px;">Focus order</h4>

  <p>A logical focus order helps visitors <strong>understand and operate</strong> Red Hat web properties. Elements need to receive focus in an order that preserves meaning, therefore the focus order should make sense and not jump around randomly.</p>

  <img src="{{ '/assets/navigation-primary/focus-order.png' | url }}" alt="Primary navigation - focus order" style="--inline-img-max-width: 1000px;">

